                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The polarized neutron beam was produced",
                "by using the reaction 2H(dpol,n)3He with a polarized",
                "deuteron beam of about 200 nA on target. The",
                "deuterium target consisted of a 3.0-cm-long gas cell",
                "which was pressurized to about 3.0 atm."
              ]
            }
          ],
