            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Data have not been corrected for finite-geometry and",
                "multiple scattering effects. However, when the",
                "unpolarized cross-section data are corrected for",
                "finite geometry, neutron and gamma absorption, and",
                "neutron multiple scattering, we find that the",
                "corrections to the A(k) coefficients were quite small",
                "compared to statistical errors."
              ]
